---
<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-900" id="solution">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <header class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        懂語意、懂情境<br />
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          比您的金牌客服更懂回話
        </span>
      </h2>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-16">
      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 text-white rounded-lg font-medium">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
            </svg>
            <span>One Dashboard</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-200">全通路一站式質檢</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            無論客人來自 LINE OA、WellyTalk 還是 Live Chat，所有對話匯總至單一平台分析。不必切換視窗，品質一目瞭然。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 opacity-10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700"></div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white rounded-lg font-medium">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>Tone & Sentiment</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-200">語意與情緒偵測</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            AI 能讀懂字裡行間的溫度。精準識別「過度承諾」、「語氣強硬」或「缺乏同理心」的回應，即時發出警報。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 opacity-10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700"></div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-500 text-white rounded-lg font-medium">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
            <span>Smart Suggestion</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-200">智能回覆優化</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            不只抓錯，更教怎麼改。AI 針對客戶問題，自動生成或潤飾最佳文字回答，讓新手也能回出資深專家的水準。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-500 opacity-10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700"></div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

